"To allow &blinken; to be more easily enjoyed by certain users, there are "
"several accessibility options built into &blinken;."
msgstr ""
"For lettere at lade visse brugere kunne glæde sig over &blinken;, er der "
"flere tilgængelighedstilvalg indbyggede i &blinken;."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:243
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid ""
#| "To view and modify the accessibility options of &blinken;, press the "
#| "<keycap>&Ctrl;</keycap> key (whilst a game is not in progress):"
